OL,5, A legal adviser to the European Court  
OL,6, of Justice has argued a ruling allowing
OL,7, Apple to avoid paying 13bn euros       
OL,8, (#11bn) in back taxes should be        
OL,9, overturned.                            
OL,11,FThe move is the latest in the          
OL,12,Flong-running saga between the EU, the  
OL,13,FUS tech giant and the Irish government.
OL,15,FThree years ago, a ruling which found  
OL,16,FApple had been given illegal tax breaks
OL,17,Fby the Irish government was overturned.
OL,19,FBut Advocate General Giovanni          
OL,20,FPitruzzella at the Court of Justice    
OL,21,Fsaid the case should be reviewed again.
